<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men nǎi zhǔ jīng bīng, yǒng gǎn xiàng qián fāng, yé sū shì yuán shuài, bù pà fēng yǔ kuáng,
 gāo jǔ shí jià chuán fú yīn, yào zǒu biàn chéng xiāng, píng yuán hé shān gǎng,
 yī gè gè róng guāng huàn fā, yī gè gè yīng zī sà shuǎng,
 fèn yǒng shā dí shàng zhàn chǎng, sǎo chú è mó, qín ná chái láng,
 hàn wèi zhēn dào, bǎo hù qún yáng,
 zhēn lǐ de qí zhì yáng qǐ lái, jī dū yǒng wèi wáng.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men nǎi zhǔ jīng bīng 迦南150</title>
